XHS-TextCard Open Source Edition

Original project:
https://github.com/geekfoxcharlie/XHS-TextCard

Official hosted version:
https://xhs-textcard.site/

This repository contains the pure frontend, zero-backend open-source edition
of XHS-TextCard. It runs locally in the browser and focuses on Markdown input,
Canvas rendering, template customization, and image export.

The official hosted version may include cloud-enhanced capabilities such as
AI-assisted formatting, API access, Feishu automation, account/quota features,
and other services that are not part of this open-source static edition.

When distributing modified copies, please keep the license notice and preserve
a reasonable attribution to the original project.
